---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Your Name" currentPage="/about">
  <div class="min-h-screen pt-24 pb-16 px-6 md:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <header class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="heading-lg mb-4">ABOUT</h1>
      </header>

      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <div class="w-32 h-32 md:w-48 md:h-48 mx-auto mb-8 rounded-full bg-gray-800 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-4xl md:text-6xl text-gray-600">?</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none text-center mb-16">
        <p class="text-body text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          欢迎来到我的个人页面。这里记录了我读过的书和创作的作品。
        </p>
        <p class="text-body text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          我相信阅读和创作是认识世界、认识自己的最好方式。每一本书都是一次旅行，每一个作品都是一次表达。
        </p>
        <p class="text-body text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          希望你能在这里找到一些有趣的东西。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="heading-md mb-8">CONNECT</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <a 
            href="https://github.com" 
            target="_blank" 
            rel="noopener noreferrer" 
            class="btn-primary"
          >
            GITHUB
          </a>
          <a 
            href="mailto:your@email.com" 
            class="btn-primary"
          >
            EMAIL
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
